<h2 id="绘制伯德图" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#绘制伯德图" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 绘制伯德图</h2>
<p>对数幅频特性曲线由各典型环节对数幅频特性叠加而成，相频特性曲线由各典型环节相频特性叠加而成。</p>
<ol>
<li>将系统传递函数写成标准形式（各环节常数项为 1），并求出其频率特性</li>
<li>确定各典型环节的转角频率，并由小到大按其顺序标在横坐标上</li>
<li>计算<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>20</mn><mi>lg</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>K</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">20\lg K</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">20</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop">l<span style="margin-right:0.01389em;">g</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span></span></span></span>，找到横坐标<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>ω</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\omega = 1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>，纵坐标为<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>20</mn><mi>lg</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>K</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">20\lg K</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">20</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop">l<span style="margin-right:0.01389em;">g</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span></span></span></span>的点</li>
<li>过点开始绘制折线，如有积分环节/二重积分环节，过该点做斜率为<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">/</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-20 dB/dec</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord">20</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mord">/</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">ec</span></span></span></span>/<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">/</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-40dB/dec</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord">40</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mord">/</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">ec</span></span></span></span>的斜线，以后每遇到一个转角频率便改变一次频率：
<ol>
<li>如遇惯性环节的转角频率，斜率增加<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">/</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-20dB/dec</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord">20</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mord">/</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">ec</span></span></span></span></li>
<li>如遇一阶微分环节的转角频率，斜率增加<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">/</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">+20dB/dec</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">+</span><span class="mord">20</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mord">/</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">ec</span></span></span></span></li>
<li>如遇振荡环节的转角频率，斜率增加<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">/</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-40dB/dec</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord">40</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mord">/</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">ec</span></span></span></span></li>
<li>如遇二阶微分环节的转角频率，斜率增加<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>40</mn><mi>d</mi><mi>B</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">/</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>c</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">+40dB/dec</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">+</span><span class="mord">40</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span><span class="mord">/</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">ec</span></span></span></span></li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>根据误差修正曲线对渐近线进行修正。</li>
</ol>
<details class="hint-container details"><summary>例题1（无积分环节的伯德图绘制）</summary>
<p>作传递函数为<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>24</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0.25</mn><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0.05</mn><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">G(s) = \frac{24(0.25s+0.5)}{(5s + 2)(0.05s + 2)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.53em;vertical-align:-0.52em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.01em;"><span style="top:-2.655em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mtight">5</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">s</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight">2</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mtight">0.05</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">s</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight">2</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.485em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">24</span><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mtight">0.25</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">s</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight">0.5</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.52em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span>的系统的 Bode 图。</p>
<p>解：化为标准形式<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>24</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0.25</mn><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0.05</mn><mi>s</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">G(s) = \frac{24(0.25s+0.5)}{(5s + 2)(0.05s + 2)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.53em;vertical-align:-0.52em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.01em;"><span style="top:-2.655em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mtight">5</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">s</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight">2</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mtight">0.05</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">s</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight">2</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.485em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">24</span><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mtight">0.25</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">s</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight">0.5</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.52em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span>，包含一个比例环节、一个一阶微分环节，两个惯性环节串联组成。</p>
<p>已知频率特性为<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>G</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>2.5</mn><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>0.025</mn><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">G(j\omega) = \frac{3(0.5j\omega + 1)}{(2.5j\omega + 1)(0.025j\omega + 1)}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">G</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">jω</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.53em;vertical-align:-0.52em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.01em;"><span style="top:-2.655em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mtight">2.5</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">jω</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mtight">0.025</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">jω</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.485em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">3</span><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mtight">0.5</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">jω</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.52em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span>，求得各环节的转角频率：</p>
<ul>
<li>一阶微分环节<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mi>j</mi><mi>ω</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1 + 0.5j\omega</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.854em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">0.5</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">jω</span></span></span></span>，有<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>ω</mi><mi>T</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">/</mi><mn>0.5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\omega_T = 1/0.5 = 2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.5806em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">T</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1/0.5</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span></li>
<li>惯性环节<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>j</mi><mn>2.5</mn><mi>ω</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\frac{1}{1 + j 2.5\omega}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.3262em;vertical-align:-0.4811em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8451em;"><span style="top:-2.655em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05724em;">j</span><span class="mord mtight">2.5</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.394em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.4811em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span>，有<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>ω</mi><mi>T</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">/</mi><mn>2.5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>0.4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\omega_T = 1/2.5 = 0.4</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.5806em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">T</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1/2.5</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">0.4</span></span></span></span></li>
<li>惯性环节<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>j</mi><mn>0.025</mn><mi>ω</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\frac{1}{1 + j 0.025\omega}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.3262em;vertical-align:-0.4811em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8451em;"><span style="top:-2.655em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05724em;">j</span><span class="mord mtight">0.025</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.394em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.4811em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span>，有<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>ω</mi><mi>T</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">/</mi><mn>0.025</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\omega_T = 1/0.025 = 40</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.5806em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">ω</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">T</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1/0.025</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">40</span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p>有<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mn>20</mn><mi>lg</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>K</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>20</mn><mi>lg</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>≈</mo><mn>9.5</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">20\lg K = 20\lg 3 \approx 9.5</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">20</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop">l<span style="margin-right:0.01389em;">g</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">K</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">20</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop">l<span style="margin-right:0.01389em;">g</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">9.5</span></span></span></span></p>
